Q: ACASS Canada Ltd在2024年每个月各机型的平均飞行小时数分别是多少？
SQL:
SELECT
        a.date_month,
        b.aircraft_model_name,
        round(( sum( a.diff_minutes )/ count(*))/ 60, 2 ) AS average_hours
FROM
        zts_plane_flight_1 a
        JOIN aircraft_details b ON a.pure_reg = b.pure_reg
WHERE
        b.supplier_id = "1015"
        AND date_month BETWEEN '2024-01'
        AND '2024-12'
        AND a.diff_minutes BETWEEN 30
        AND 1080
GROUP BY
        a.date_month,
        b.aircraft_model_name
ORDER BY
        date_month ASC,
        aircraft_model_name DESC;
actual_SQL:
SELECT
        a.date_month,
        b.aircraft_model_name,
        round(( sum( a.diff_minutes )/ count(*))/ 60, 2 ) AS average_hours
FROM
        zts_plane_flight_1 a
        JOIN aircraft_details b ON a.pure_reg = b.pure_reg
WHERE
        b.supplier_id = "1015"
        AND date_month BETWEEN '2024-01'
        AND '2024-12'
        AND a.diff_minutes BETWEEN 30
        AND 1080
GROUP BY
        a.date_month,
        b.aircraft_model_name
ORDER BY
        date_month ASC,
        aircraft_model_name DESC;
